<td rowspan="2"><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">/a/</span> or <span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">/ɐ/</span><sup>1</sup></td>
